Global Endoscope Radiofrequency Ablation RFA Market Insights
Endoscope Radiofrequency Ablation RFA Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Endoscope Radiofrequency Ablation RFA Market Overview
The Endoscope Radiofrequency Ablation (RFA) Market is poised to reach significant growth, driven by rising demand for minimally invasive procedures and advancements in endoscopic technologies. As of 2023, the market value was estimated at $2.8 billion, and it is projected to grow at a CAGR of 7.5%, reaching around $4.8 billion by 2030. The increasing prevalence of chronic conditions such as gastrointestinal diseases, cancer, and obesity is further fueling this market. Additionally, the preference for outpatient surgeries and the growing healthcare investments in endoscopic devices are key drivers behind the market expansion.

